    The season introduced Trent Nielsen, Annie Foley, Joe Brandl, Andrea Lopez, and Cassidy Flynn to the franchise. It was one of the show's shorter runs — Naked and Afraid XL had by this point spun off to run in parallel, drawing the network's more experienced survivalists into that longer-format sister series while Season 5 focused on newer faces.
